<html>
    <head>
        <title>Business Accounting Formula Suite</title>
    </head>
    <body>
        <h1><b>WELCOME</b></h1>
        <h2>TO THE</h2>
        <h2>BUSINESS ACCOUNTING</h2>
        <h2>FORMULA SUITE</h2>
        <br />
        
        <p><h3>1. Basic Accounting Equation</h3></p>
        <p>assets = liabilities + equity</p>
        <p>a = l + e</p>
        
        <p>Please enter your amount of liabilities (l):
            <input type="number" id="bael" />
            </input>
            <br />
        </p>
        
        <p>Please enter your amount of equity (e):
            <input type="number" id="baee" />
            </input>
            <br />
        </p>
        
        <input type="submit" onclick="bae()">
        </input>
        
        <br />
        <br />
        <br />
        
        <p><h3>2. Net Income Equation</h3></p>
        <p>income = revenues - expenses</p>
        <p>i = r - e</p>
        
        <p>Please enter your total amount of revenues (r):
            <input type="number" id="nier" />
            </input>
            <br />
        </p>
        
        <p>Please enter your total amount of expenses (e):
            <input type="number" id="niee" />
            </input>
            <br />
        </p>
        <input type="submit" onclick="nie()">
        </input>
        
        <br />
        <br />
        <br />
        
        <p><h3>3. Break-Even Point Equation</h3></p>
        <p>break-even point = fixed costs / (sales price per unit - variable cost per unit)</p>
        <p>b = f / (p - c)</p>
        
        <p>Please enter your total amount of fixed costs (f):
            <input type="number" id="bepf" />
            </input>
            <br />
        </p>
        
        <p>Please enter your sales price per unit (p):
            <input type="number" id="bepp" />
            </input>
            <br />
        </p>
        
        <p>Please enter your variable costs per unit (c):
            <input type="number" id="bepc" />
            </input>
            <br />
        </p>
        
        <input type="submit" onclick="bep()">
        </input>
        
        <br />
        <br />
        <br />
        
        <p><h3>4. Cash Ratio</h3></p>
        <p>cash ratio = cash & equivalents / current liabilities</p>
        <p>r = c / l</p>
        
        <p>Please enter your total amount of cash and cash equivalents (c):
            <input type="number" id="crec" />
            </input>
            <br />
        </p>
        
        <p>Please enter your total amount of current liabilities (l):
            <input type="number" id="crel" />
            </input>
            <br />
        </p>
        
        <input type="submit" onclick="cre()">
        </input>
        
        <br />
        <br />
        <br />
        
        <p><h3>5. Profit Margin</h3></p>
        <p>profit margin = net income / total sales</p>
        <p>m = i / s;</p>
        
        <p>Please enter your net income (i):</p>
            <input type="number" id="pmei" />
            </input>
            <br />
        
        <p>Please enter your total of sales (s):</p>
            <input type="number" id="pmes" />
            </input>
            <br />
            <br />
        
        <input type="submit" onclick="pme()">
        </input>
        
        <br />
        <br />
        <br />
        
        <p><h3>6. COGS</h3></p>
        <p>cost of goods sold = beginning inventory + amount of purchases - ending inventory</p>
        <p>c = b + p - e;</p>
        
        <p>Please enter your beginning inventory (b):</p>
            <input type="number" id="cogsb" />
            </input>
            <br />
        
        <p>Please enter your total amount of purchases (p):</p>
            <input type="number" id="cogsp" />
            </input>
            <br />
        
        <p>Please enter your ending inventory (e):</p>
            <input type="number" id="cogse" />
            </input>
            <br />
            <br />
            
        <input type="submit" onclick="cogs()">
        </input>
        
        <br />
        <br />
        <br />
        
        <p><h3>7. Debt-To-Equity Ratio</h3></p>
        <p>debt-to-equity ratio = liabilities / equity</p>
        <p>r = l / e;</p>
        
        <p>Please enter your total amount of liabilities (l):</p>
            <input type="number" id="dterl" />
            </input>
            <br />
        
        <p>Please enter your total amount of equity (e):</p>
            <input type="number" id="dtere" />
            </input>
            <br />
            <br />
        
        <input type="submit" onclick="dter()">
        </input>
        
        <br />
        <br />
        <br />
        
        <p><h3>8. Simple Interest Calculator</h3></p>
        <p>ending amount = principle × (1 + (interest rate × time))</p>
        <p>a = p * (1 + (r * t));</p>
        
        <p>Please enter the principle amount (p):</p>
            <input type="number" id="sicp" />
            </input>
            <br />
        
        <p>Please enter the interest rate (as a decimal) (r):</p>
            <input type="number" id="sicr" />
            </input>
            <br />
        
        <p>Please enter the amount of time (in years) (t):</p>
            <input type="number" id="sict" />
            </input>
            <br />
            <br />
        
        <input type="submit" onclick="sic()">
        </input>
        
        <br />
        <br />
        <br />
        
        <p><h3>9. Compound Interest Calculator</h3></p>
        <p>ending amount = principle × ((1 +(interest rate / number of times compounded)) ^ (number of times compounded × time))</p>
        <p>a = p × ((1 + (r / n)) ^ (n × t));</p>
        
        <p>Please enter the principle amount (p):</p>
            <input type="number" id="cicp" />
            </input>
            <br />
        
        <p>Please enter the interest rate (as a decimal) (r):</p>
            <input type="number" id="cicr" />
            </input>
            <br />
        
        <p>Please enter the number of times compounded per year (n):</p>
            <input type="number" id="cicn" />
            </input>
            <br />
        
        <p>Please enter the amount of time (in years) (t):</p>
            <input type="number" id="cict" />
            </input>
            <br />
            <br />
        
        <input type="submit" onclick="cic()">
        </input>
        
        <br />
        <br />
        <br />
    </body>
</html>

